{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8da6b6d99a","title":"掉念布曼增迪的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f1d13c82ae","index":0,"year":1953,"month":9,"day":24,"articleId":"8da6b6d99a"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"262a473dc4","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8da6b6d99a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"布曼增迪，即冈奇金·布曼增迪，逝世前任蒙古人民革命党政治局委员、蒙古人民共和国大人民呼拉尔主席团主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"791481793e","type":"title","text":"掉念布曼增迪的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8da6b6d99a"},{"id":"262a473dc4","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古人民共和国大人民呼拉尔主席团：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8da6b6d99a"},{"id":"ab3c6d4f3f","type":"paragraph","text":"我以悲痛的心情获悉冈奇金·布曼增迪同志逝世的消息。风奇金·布曼增迪同志是蒙古人民革命运动杰出的战士、乔巴山元帅的亲密战友，他为蒙古人民的革命事业贡献了自己的全部生命","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8da6b6d99a"},{"id":"97d7da7691","type":"paragraph","text":"习奇金·布曼增通同志的浙世是蒙古人民的重大损失。我谨代表中国人民、中国政府并以我自己的名义，谨向您们，并通过您们向蒙古人民致最深切的衰停。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8da6b6d99a"},{"id":"18a581ce63","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国中央人民政府主席毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8da6b6d99a"},{"id":"2ec9847eba","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年九月二十四日于北京","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8da6b6d99a"}],"page":{"id":"5b7fd6ccf1","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8da6b6d99a","start":354,"end":354}}}},"__N_SSG":true}